data.description: Privacy, Privacy! Home sits on almost an acre of land. Very well maintained split level home, New Roof with 3 beds 2 full baths. Hardwood floors throughout the family room and New laminated wood flooring in the kitchen, hallway, Master bedroom. Masterbath has large soaking tub and separate shower. Make this your home and enjoy nature.
data.whatILove: Very family oriented neighborhood, quite and peaceful. Backyard has a deck where you can enjoy your coffee every morning surrounded by nature.
